Light, fresh, home

Today’s amenities and plenty of natural light highlight these modern, urban apartments!

901 Main is located at... 901 Main Street! This three-story, mixed-use urban development offers two levels of one and two-bedroom apartments above first floor commercial space in the middle of the action.

Residents will enjoy inviting living spaces with plenty of daylight (including every bedroom!) and in-unit, full-size washers and dryers. Residents will also be able to choose units that are appointed with upgrades including kitchen backsplashes and outdoor balconies. On-site parking is provided.

Both the 1-bedroom and 2-bedroom units are designed with large windows that bathe each unit in natural light. And although it may sound silly, each bedroom at 901 Main has a window! (Not all new apartment complexes do). Each apartment contains full-size washers and dryers and its own water heater. Premier units are also available offering upgraded appliances, tile kitchen backsplashes and private balconies for outdoor relaxing.

We are pet friendly!

When choosing a place to call home, what could be better than to be pet-friendly AND located across from the Whitney Bark Park?! Enjoy a beautiful summer evening or a new-fallen snow with your four-legged friend at the year-round Bark Park, a mere 200 feet away from your front door.

Pets are welcome at 901 Main for a small additional fee, detailed below. Waste facilities will be provided on-site for residents.

Details & Ammenities

Indoor parking is $75/month on a first-reserved, first-served basis.
Outdoor surface parking is provided at no charge.
Monthly pet fees are $25 for cats and $50 for dogs
(with one-time refundable pet damage deposit at signing).
Hi-speed wifi available at $75/month, with 149 free HD TV channels.
Water/electric/gas service is each tenant’s responsibility.
